-------------------------------------------------------CCK FIELD PLUGIN FOR SEBLOD 2.0 CCK FOR JOOMLA 1.7.X-------------------------------------------------------Version: 2.1.2Name: SD Field ConcatAuthor: Simon Dowdles - www.onestuckpixel.comTwitter: @simondowdles--------------Description--------------Concatenates any cck fields, plain text values & limited pre-defined variables into one value. Ideal for unique titles--------------Instructions--------------> Plain text to appear in square brackets like [plain text here]. Fields enclosed with # like #field_name# and predefined variables like $date, $time, $username & $userid> Field Separator determines the character used to glue all values together. Use value 'ns' should you not want a separator. Default is a space.> You can specidy the date format string, which accepts any valid PHP date() formatting syntax. Defaults to Y-m-d> Example: [Article created by]||$username||[on]||$date||[in category ID]||#art_catid#> Will result in: "Article created by Simon Dowdles on 2011-08-26 in category ID 9" where I would have used no field separator character, and therefore it defaulted to a space. ------------- Notes------------- > SD Field Concat will soon be update to run on Joomla! 2.5.1 where SEBLOD CCK class names have changed as a result of the new class autoloading in Joomla! 2.5.x ------------Contribute------------  If you'd like to contribute to this project, please request a fork, I'll be more than happy!